==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Swimmer
<hw>Swim"mer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
swims.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Far.)</fld> <def>A protuberance on the leg of a
horse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A swimming bird; one of the
natatores.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Little swimmer</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>a
phalarope.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swimmeret</ent>⟦br⟧
